item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Taylor Swift - 1989 (Taylor's Version) (Deluxe) (2023) *UPDATED NOV 6 MASTER* Qobuz Hi-Res 24bit 48kHz
item.description:
The original master of this album that went out everywhere, both physical and digital was defective. It had a buzz/electronic noise at 15.7kHz or thereabouts on the vocal track(s) on nearly every song. They've gone back and attempted to fix it and sent the new master out today (maybe yesterday) digitally. It's not completely fixed but it's in a much better state this time.

The link below is a fresh rip from Qobuz from an hour ago. It is the new version, and I have compared the spectrogram to confirm the differences.
